prompt.title: Embedding for AI-Friendly Markup: The Book Language
prompt.content: The Book language is a human-understandable markup language for writing AI applications such as chatbots, knowledge bases, agents, avatars, translators, and automations. It is based on markdown and designed to be easy to read and write.
